a baby girl
was born>

15
00:01:11,379 --> 00:01:16,379
(泣き声)
分かった 分かった…｡

16
00:01:19,553 --> 00:01:24,425
(金太)かうぇえらしいのう｡

17
00:01:24,425 --> 00:01:27,728
(泣き声)

18
00:01:27,728 --> 00:01:29,730
<Her family's business➡

19
00:01:29,730 --> 00:01:33,534
made traditional Japanese sweets>

20
00:01:33,534 --> 00:01:43,010
♬～

21
00:01:43,010 --> 00:01:47,510
<The girl was named Yasuko>

22
00:01:51,352 --> 00:01:54,852
(ひさ)あっ こんにちは｡
どうも｡

23
00:01:57,525 --> 00:02:00,428
<This is the very beginning of➡

24
00:02:00,428 --> 00:02:06,534
a family story
that spans one hundred years.➡

25
00:02:06,534 --> 00:02:13,034
100年の物語の始まり 始まり>

26
